name: .CUID File Extension
summary: Learn about .CUID files and view a list of programs that open them.

instructions: At this time, there is no known program that opens Baidu CUID files. According to users' reports, you can delete the baidu folder and baidu.cuid file it contains from your smartphone without affecting your phone or its installed apps.
